commit.message: Bump version for release
Update changelog

Allow environment copy to take a passed-in transaction (#247)

Add a patch that adds two new C lmdb APIs `mdb_env_copy{fd,}3` that take a transaction argument. The copy will have the contents of the database from the view of the transaction. This requires `compact=True`.

Modify setup to apply the patch unless `LMDB_PURE` environment variable is set.

Cleanup CI.
